# Diamonds Project Environment Configuration
# ==================================
# This file contains NON-SECRET configuration only.
# All secrets (API keys, private keys, tokens) should be stored in HashiCorp Vault.
#
# To set up secrets in Vault:
# 1. Start the DevContainer (docker-compose will start Vault automatically)
# 2. Run: .devcontainer/scripts/vault-init.sh
# 3. Run: .devcontainer/scripts/setup/migrate-secrets-to-vault.sh
# 4. Or manually add secrets using: vault kv put secret/dev/YOUR_SECRET_KEY value=YOUR_SECRET_VALUE
#
# To retrieve secrets during development:
# Run: .devcontainer/scripts/vault-fetch-secrets.sh
#
# For more information, see: docs/devs/VAULT_SETUP.md

